RollTable.name: Ace Trainer
RollTable.description:
An adult who frequently travels around the
world to meet new trainers and take part in
Pokemon League competitions.

Specialization Strong, evolved, and diverse Pokemon.

RollTable.name: Archaeologist
RollTable.description:
Lanky men and women who excitedly jump
around when they find fossils.

Specialization Fossil Pokemon

RollTable.name: Aroma Lady
RollTable.description:
A young woman surrounded by swirling
flower petals.
Specialization Grass-Type Pokemon; Pokemon that are
associated with flowers.

RollTable.name: Artist
RollTable.description:
An old man wearing berets and carrying art
supplies. or A young woman holding a
paintbrush covered in paint.

Specialization Pokemon that can learn Copycat and/or
Mimic; Pokemon related to the arts.

RollTable.name: Backpacker
RollTable.description:
Young adults who travel across wide open
spaces with large backpacks and camping
supplies.

Man or woman with a chef's hat, tray, and
apron. Sometimes seen living in pink trailers
with all of their cooking utensils and
appliances. May ask for ingredients or
assistance.

Specialization
Pokemon related to food or food
preparation; Grass- and Fire-Type Pokemon

Man or woman found lounging on the

RollTable.description:

women.

cuteness
